        <div xml:id="TK150">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>aṟaṉvaraiyā ṉalla ceyiṉum piṟaṉvaraiyāḷ</l>
<l>peṇmai nayavāmai naṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Though a man perform no virtuous deeds and commit (every) vice, it will be well if he desire not the womanhood of her who is within the limit (of the house) of another.</l>
            </lg>
